properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 9:58AM CST until January 6 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to 30 knots and
waves 2 to 4 feet expected.

* WHERE...Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN, Grand Marais to
Taconite Harbor MN and Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN.

* WHEN...Until noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Mariners, especially those operating smaller vessels, should
avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY... ...GALE WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 10 AM CST THIS MORNING
